# Authoritative quirks catalog — 136 byte-exact cases ground-truthed on PHP 8.5.5.
# Produced by the research workflow (independently reproduced by OTP 28 :re, 0 mismatches).
# Format: base64(input) <TAB> category <TAB> why.  Loader uses field 1 (the input);
# fields 2-3 are human/diff documentation. Comment lines start with '#'.
